title: Microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation, preparation method and application thereof
abstract: The invention discloses a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation, a preparation method and application thereof. The preparation consists of the following components in part by weight: 1 to 30 parts of pesticide microcapsules and 70 to 99 parts of nutrient substance. The preparation method mainly comprises the following steps of: after fully dissolving a pesticide with a solvent, adding a wall material monomer into solution and mixing uniformly; transporting a mixture into a shear dispersion reaction kettle which is filled with smashed capsule bodies; stirring the mixture and the capsule bodies so that the capsules fully absorb the solution; performing a shear dispersion reaction to form capsules; performing solid-liquid separation and drying to prepare the pesticide microcapsules; adding the nutrient substances into the pesticide microcapsules; and fully stirring and uniformly mixing to prepare the microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation. By using the microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation and the preparation method, the problems of the chemical compatibility and the physical stability of the conventional insecticide-fertilizer preparation in the same system are solved effectively. A product of the invention has the advantages of: shielding and slow-releasing functions, high chemical compatibility and physical stability, lasting pesticide effect, natural degradability, no environment pollution, low use cost and simple production process.
claims: 1. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation calculates with weight ratio, by 1～30 part pesticide micro capsule, and 70～99 parts composition of nutritive substance.

2. a kind of microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation according to claim 1 is characterized in that described pesticide micro capsule, calculates with weight ratio, and by 1～30 part agricultural chemicals, 10～65 parts solvent, 1～11 part wall material monomer, 30～80 parts utricule is formed.

4. according to claim 1 or 2 or 3 described a kind of microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparations, it is characterized in that described agricultural chemicals comprises any one or more mixing in following:
      Avrmectin, Volaton, this tick of poison, first dimension salt, pyrethrin, nimbin, Celastrus angulatus, tubatoxin, benbbensulfuronmethyl, pyrazosulfuronmethyl, acetochlor, the third careless amine, propisochlor, mefenacet, Butachlor technical 92, brassinolide.

5. according to claim 1 or 2 or 3 described a kind of microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparations, it is characterized in that described solvent comprises any one or more mixing in following:
      Turps, eucalyptus oil, pimelinketone, dimethylbenzene, ethyl acetate, sherwood oil.

6. according to claim 1 or 2 or 3 described a kind of microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparations, it is characterized in that described wall material monomer comprises any one or more mixing in following:
      Tolylene diisocyanate, hexamethylene diisocyanate, dimethylbenzene isocyanic ester, polymethylene polyphenyl isocyanate, p-phthaloyl chloride, phthalyl chloride, hexanedioyl chlorine, azelaoyl chloride, the two acyl chlorides of 12 carbon, lemon acyl chlorides, 1,4 hexanaphthene diacid chloride.

7. according to claim 1 or 2 or 3 described a kind of microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparations, it is characterized in that described utricule, comprise any one or more mixing in following:
      Cyclodextrine, flyash, kiln ash, diatomite, activated carbon.

8. according to claim 1 or 3 described a kind of microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparations, it is characterized in that described nutritive substance comprises any one or more mixing in following:
      Amino acid solution, yellow humic acid salt brine solution, fertilizer, humic acids, nitrogen, Vanadium Pentoxide in FLAKES, potassium oxide, calcium, magnesium, sulphur, zinc, boron, molybdenum, manganese, copper, iron.
9. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation is as the application of sterilant.
10. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation is as herbicide applications.
11. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation is as the application of plant-growth regulator
12. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation is as the application of foliage fertilizer.
13. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation is as the application of fertilizer.
14. a microcapsule insecticide-fertilizer preparation is as the application of organic-inorganic compound mixed fertilizer.
